      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * The Spacious Mind</b>\n</p><p><b>Spacious Mind</b>,<br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pseudonym\">pseudonym</a> of Nick Milicev <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, a computer chess aficionado and collector of <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">dedicated chess computers</a> as well as chess programs for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home_computer\">home-</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_computer\">personal computers</a>. He maintains <i>The Spacious Mind</i> sites <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> with a lot of informations about chess computers and programs, referred from multiple <a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">CPW</a> sites on these topics.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2008_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2008 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2008_...\">2008 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2008 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schachcomputer.info/forum/f11/schachcomputer-vergleich-zu-alte-computerschach-spiele-1948-2.html\">Turnier: Schachcomputer vergleich zu alte Computerschach Spiele</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Schachcomputer.info Forum</a>, August 12, 2008 (German)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=4546\">It's Magic</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, November 23, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Mysticum&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Mysticum (page does not exist)\">Mysticum</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schachcomputer.info/forum/showthread.php?t=3531\">Studie: Schachspielen mit ein 286er 12 MHz Laptop</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Schachcomputer.info Forum</a>, May 22, 2010 (German)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=6425\">Some food for thought</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, November 11, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> vs. <a href=\"/ChessMachine\" title=\"ChessMachine\">Tasc CM32 512K</a> <a href=\"/The_King\" title=\"The King\">The King 2.2</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=7306\">Gavon 2 Chess Test Scores</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, July 23, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Gavon\" title=\"Gavon\">Gavon</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=7381\">Phoenix Systems Revelation Test Scores</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, August 29, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Revelation\" title=\"Revelation\">Revelation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=7490\">Gavon 3 Chess Test Scores</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, November 02, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=8120\">Where is Nick?</a> by dedicate computers, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, November 12, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=8206\">Nick is alive and well!</a> by Reinfeld, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, January 13, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=8211\">Spacious-Mind Swiss Chess Computer League - Div 4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, January 17, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=9277\">Millennium Chess Genius and The King tests</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>, December 22, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Millennium_ChessGenius\" title=\"Millennium ChessGenius\">Millennium ChessGenius</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=9287\">Millennium - The King - Best Personality Competition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>, December 25, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Millennium_The_King\" title=\"Millennium The King\">Millennium The King</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=9403&amp;start=16\">DOSBox Windows 95 for Chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">The Spacious Mind</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">HIARCS Forum</a>, March 09, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Bringer\" title=\"Bringer\">Bringer</a>, <a href=\"/Chessmaster\" title=\"Chessmaster\">Chessmaster</a>, ...</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.spacious-mind.com/index.html\">The Spacious Mind</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.spacious-mind.com/html/collection.html\">The Spacious Mind - Electronic Chess Computer Collection</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.spacious-mind.com/html/computers.html\">The Spacious Mind Old Home Computers &amp; Emulators Collection</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/spacious\">spacious - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/mind\">mind - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mind\">Mind from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Spacious_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href